description:
Bastion attacks with only one goal in mind: destroy Hope! The X-Men battle to save all mutantkind! Cable struggles to rescue X-Force!

By Mike Carey, Esad Ribic, Zeb Wells, Ibraim Roberson, Matt Fraction and Terry Dodson.

Collects : X-Force (2008) #28 - X-Men: Second Coming (2010) #02 - Uncanny X-Men - The Heroic Age (2010)

Five new mutants have been sighted around the world – is this the rebirth of mutantkind? Hope, Storm, Rogue and Iceman go in search of the future of the X-Men in a new story, ‘The Five Lights’!

By Matt Fraction and Whilce Portacio

Includes material reprinted from Uncanny X-Men #526-528.
